back when they were teens.

17:50.320 --> 17:54.643
He was working-class
and she was Louisiana royalty.

17:54.690 --> 17:58.023
My plan is to get her
on the water before the summer.

17:58.070 --> 17:59.697
Id love to take you
out on it.

18:02.740 --> 18:07.200
You know, my daddy,
he lived for the water.

18:07.250 --> 18:10.287
The irony being, my mama,
like your daddy,

18:10.340 --> 18:11.955
lived for the land.

18:12.000 --> 18:15.709
