to hers.

18:17.680 --> 18:18.965
Well, thats all very nice,

18:19.010 --> 18:20.966
but whats it got
to do with me?

18:22.470 --> 18:24.176
My daddys superstitious.

18:25.310 --> 18:27.437
He said...

18:27.480 --> 18:29.186
"Always toast a new partnership

18:29.230 --> 18:31.551
as close to the water
as pOSSlble."

18:31.610 --> 18:33.566
He believed people
could pretend

18:33.610 --> 18:35.737
to be something else
on dry ground

18:35.780 --> 18:38.567
