Miss Effie,

22:50.030 --> 22:51.657
thats not how
I remember it--

22:51.700 --> 22:53.520
Why would we want
to help you?

22:57.000 --> 23:00.072
Because I am donating

23:00.120 --> 23:04.830
10% of my profits
to the St. Agnes Society.

23:05.920 --> 23:08.047
Well...

23:08.090 --> 23:10.581
