26:32.210 --> 26:33.495
Nothing.

26:42.930 --> 26:45.387
Got me questioning
whether I could do this or not.

26:49.230 --> 26:50.686
Like, for real.

26:54.400 --> 26:56.311
Am I good for that boy?

27:01.910 --> 27:06.495
You are the best thing that ever
happened to that little boy.

27:08.410 --> 27:09.570
Appreciate it.

27:11.250 --> 27:12.456
Well, enough of this.

27:13.790 --> 27:15.587
No more Darla.

27:15.630 --> 27:17.666
No more Davis.

27:17.720 --> 27:20.371
-No more Remy.
-All right, now.

27:20.430 --> 27:22.136
