that you wanted to.

30:44.590 --> 30:47.502
Ill take care
of the deliveries.

30:47.550 --> 30:49.336
Thank you, baby.

30:51.430 --> 30:53.170
Why dont you go home
and get you some rest.

30:53.220 --> 30:54.676
Because you want
to be feeling good

30:54.720 --> 30:56.347
when we walk in that store
seeing these pies

30:56.390 --> 30:59.393
