31:53.780 --> 31:56.157
Has Micah seen it?
The video?

31:56.200 --> 31:58.577
Because Im wondering
if its helping or hurting.

32:00.460 --> 32:01.950
Thats all I ask.

32:02.000 --> 32:05.083
Keep him foremost
in mind, yeah?

