to justify my presence.

33:56.910 --> 34:00.983
Okay? Youre... youre black,
but the son of a celebrity,

34:01.030 --> 34:03.578
so its okay.

34:03.620 --> 34:06.669
Youre black,
but you have money, so you...

34:14.420 --> 34:16.001
