34:22.100 --> 34:23.260
Okay.

34:25.390 --> 34:27.722
Well try it.

34:27.770 --> 34:30.398
For a little while.

34:30.440 --> 34:32.180
But if anything
goes wrong...

34:34.740 --> 34:35.934
Okay, thank you.

34:37.110 --> 34:38.270
Thank you.

34:46.830 --> 34:49.071
