35:35.170 --> 35:37.627
Definitely was acting
brand-new.

35:37.670 --> 35:40.298
But you aint got
a bad bone in your body.

35:40.340 --> 35:41.637
You hear me?

35:41.680 --> 35:42.965
Yeah.

35:44.470 --> 35:46.051
Can I help?

36:10.120 --> 36:12.281
Oh, hey.

36:12.330 --> 36:14.412
Hey, Viclq.
